Mon père, ce héros.;;1991;;NC;;Comedy,Drama,Romance;;6.1;;Gérard Lauzier;;Gérard Depardieu,Marie Gillain,Catherine Jacob,Charlotte de Turckheim,Gérard Hérold,Patrick Mille,Benoît Allemane,Harriet Batchelor,Sultan Beeharry,Éric Berger,Franck-Olivier Bonnet,Yan Brian,François Bruhat,Koomaren Chetty,Thierry Der'ven,Marpessa Djian,Philippe François,Evelyne Lagesse;;Veronique, living with her divorced mother, is going on holiday to Mauritius with her father. To impress a local boy, Benjamin, she manages to complicate the situation by making up stories about her father. She presents him as her lover, a mercenary and even a secret agent which gets her into trouble and then her father has to start playing along...;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0102465/